Summary of columns contained and what the abbreviations stand for

General

season_id: season code (e.g. 22023 → 2023–24)
game_id: game identifier
game_date: date played
season_type: Regular / Playoffs / Pre-season / Play-In
matchup_home / matchup_away: matchup text (“LAL vs. DEN”, “DEN @ LAL”)
wl_home / wl_away: win or loss flag
min: total team minutes (usually 240 = 48×5)
video_available_home / video_available_away: highlight flag

Team Identifiers

team_id_home / team_id_away: team numeric ID
team_abbreviation_home / team_abbreviation_away: 3-letter team code (e.g. LAL)
team_code_home / team_code_away: internal team code (redundant)
team_name_home / team_name_away: full team name

Shooting & Scoring

fgm: field goals made
fga: field goals attempted
fg_pct: field goal percentage
fg3m: 3-point field goals made
fg3a: 3-point field goals attempted
fg3_pct: 3-point field goal percentage
ftm: free throws made
fta: free throws attempted
ft_pct: free throw percentage
pts: total points scored
plus_minus: point differential (team points − opponent points)

Rebounding & Defense

oreb: offensive rebounds
dreb: defensive rebounds
reb: total rebounds
ast: assists
stl: steals
blk: blocks
tov: turnovers
pf: personal fouls

Advanced / Situational Stats

pts_paint: points scored in the paint
pts_2nd_chance: second-chance points
pts_fb: fast-break points
largest_lead: largest lead held in the game
lead_changes: number of lead changes
times_tied: number of times score was tied
team_turnovers: turnovers committed by team (non-forced)
total_turnovers: total turnovers (all types)
team_rebounds: total team rebounds
pts_off_to: points scored off turnovers

Per-Period Scoring (from line_score)

pts_qtr1: points in 1st quarter
pts_qtr2: points in 2nd quarter
pts_qtr3: points in 3rd quarter
pts_qtr4: points in 4th quarter
pts_ot1: points in 1st overtime
pts_ot2: points in 2nd overtime
pts_ot3: points in 3rd overtime
pts_ot4: points in 4th overtime
pts_ot5: points in 5th overtime
pts_ot6: points in 6th overtime
pts_ot7: points in 7th overtime
pts_ot8: points in 8th overtime
pts_ot9: points in 9th overtime
pts_ot10: points in 10th overtime
